      Look 
      %a(href="https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/wiki/User-Scripts")here 
      for more information.
    

.row
  .col-md-6
    %h4
      %i.fa.fa-eye
      High quality video output
    %p
      mpv has an OpenGL based video output that is capable of many features
      loved by videophiles, such as video scaling with popular high quality
      algorithms, color management, frame timing, interpolation, HDR, and more.

  .col-md-6
    %h4
      %i.fa.fa-tachometer
      GPU video decoding

    %p
      mpv leverages the FFmpeg hwaccel APIs to support VDPAU, VAAPI, DXVA2, VDA
      and VideoToolbox video decoding acceleration.

.row
  .col-md-6
    %h4
      %i.fa.fa-cubes
      Embeddable
    %p
      A straightforward
      %a(href="https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/blob/master/libmpv/client.h")C API
      was designed from the ground up to make mpv usable as a library and
      facilitate easy integration into other applications.

  .col-md-6
    %h4
      %i.fa.fa-wrench
      Active development
    %p
      mpv is under active development, focusing on code refactoring and
      cleanups as well as adding features. Want a feature?
      %a(href="https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/issues" target="_blank")
        Post a patch or request it!

